      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair, functional condition and would make a suitable choice for someone seeking a budget-friendly option. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some paint fading on the hood, and a small dent on the rear bumper. Inside, the upholstery has visible wear and some staining from regular use. While the car is currently drivable, the engine is showing signs of age and will likely need a comprehensive tune-up or minor repairs in the near future to maintain reliability.",
