    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior, reflects a standard of care synonymous with showroom quality. Meticulously maintained and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, this specimen offers an unrivaled ownership experience for the discerning driver who demands perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
