    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This 2003 BMW M3 (E46) is a preserved example of high-revving atmospheric engineering. At its heart is the S54B32 inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double VANOS system, delivering a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. This chassis is mechanically sorted with documented rod bearing replacement and proactive rear subframe reinforcement. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission remains crisp, paired with a factory M-Variable Differential Lock for superior lateral traction. Every suspension component maintains its original kinematic integrity, offering the precise feedback and chassis balance the E46 is renowned for. This is a turn-key, investment-grade specimen for the discerning collector.",
